close_reason: Tests passed and semantic indexing correctly batches to Ollama /api/embed endpoint
body: "Using /api/embeddings did not support batching correctly for qwen3-embedding:0.6b in Ollama. Switching to /api/embed allows us to pass multiple inputs and get multiple vectors back, fixing the cardinality mismatch error."
